<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.hiddencircle.org/view_profile.php?num=78">Splack Dwarf High Priest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=besrikarle>Besrikarle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 218<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/23/02 9:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_rip.gif" align=absmiddle>  .</span><hr size=1> Run part way there, spawn some traps.. zone it. Repeat that about 4 or 5 times, forget how many traps exactly. Then, invis up and run to the room. Run right up to the 4-arms and drop down into the pit. Back up so your in the corner at the back of the C formation. Once there, your safe. 4-arms will not aggro from you being below them. Then, kill the two closest remains. If you try killing the outter 2 you will aggro wailing shades. Once you get your frame, just invis up and run back out.. probably training traps in the process. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showPrevMessage?topicID=1503.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showNextMessage?topicID=1503.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.emailToFriend?topicID=1503.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.threadControl?topicID=1503.topic><img src=http://w